title: Annual Media Conference 2021
body:
This Thursday, Deutsche Bank published its results for the fourth quarter and the full year 2020. CEO Christian Sewing and CFO James von Moltke presented the details at a virtual Annual Media Conference. Afterwards, they answered questions from journalists.
